lack; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1eafp g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">CSKA Moscow t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh CSKA Moscow. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/co-doi-bong-chi-25-trieu-bang-mua-trai-dep-tuyen-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>CSKA Moscow t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Alex Golovin cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u00f4, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp Golovin \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 2 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Golovin, M.U c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus-176-188909.html\" target=\"_blank\">CSKA Moscow t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</span> v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Golovin l\u00ean 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1eafp g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ngoi Golovin\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Nga-vs-Saudi-Arabia-bang-A-World-Cup-2018-Tuyet-voi-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Golovin l\u00ean 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga l\u00ean 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Juventus c\u00f2n tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Tuttosport, CSKA Moscow \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec7c Golovin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"465","checkdouble":"189263"},{"date":"15:46 22/06","title":"Chelsea gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng \"h\u00e0ng hot\" Seria A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/4/8/trung-ve-phil-jones-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap CLB AS Roma v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League, trung v\u1ec7 Kostas Manolas \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, Chelsea.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng Kostas Manolas</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. N\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 theo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p Kostas Manolas v\u1edbi CLB AS Roma.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/11/Chelsea-muon-co-Kostas-Manolas-tu-AS-Roma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kostas Manolas t\u1eeb AS Roma</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 26, Kostas Manolas \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 - m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111ang l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico v\u00e0 gi\u00fap CLB n\u00e0y l\u1eadp&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u khi l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18. Manolas c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1eeba qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a Manolas v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 trong kho\u1ea3ng 36-38 tri\u1ec7u euro.&nbsp;Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Manolas.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Manolas, Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eafp ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. S\u1edf d\u0129 The Blues \u01b0a d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Serie A b\u1edfi HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea v\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Maurizio Sarri c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, BL\u0110 Chelsea c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng &ldquo;gi\u1ea3i ng\u00e2n&rdquo; h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/21/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-voi-gia-31-trieu-bang-172-189240.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas-172-189078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-fabregas-172-189078.html\">Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Fabregas</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic thay Cesc Fabregas, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"464","checkdouble":"189265"},{"date":"15:43 22/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Brazil vs Costa Rica 19h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/link-xem-brazil-vs-costa-rica.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 2-1<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (3'); C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (10'); Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (41')<hr>\r\n<br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1o si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m HAGL khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh Vuong ghi ban tran Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap HAGL t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt ph\u00fat, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap HAGL d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 41, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m65 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"463","checkdouble":"189267"},{"date":"16:09 22/06","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Paul Pogba l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Pogba \u0111\u1ec3 thay Iniesta</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay CLB Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a I8 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi BHL Barca c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n HLV Ernesto Valverde trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-225-juve-tinh-gay-soc-voi-pogba.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon th\u00ec&nbsp; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Paul Pogba, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 HLV Valverde tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Nou Camp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n khi m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Man Utd trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eb1m &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i kh\u00f3 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n r\u1ebb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Theo t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba t\u1eeb Juventus v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Barca, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pogba, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo s\u00e1t Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Christian Eriksen. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n 2 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana n\u1ebfu v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca</span><br>\r\nTottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Spurs c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-189259.html\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span><br>\r\nJuventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"462","checkdouble":"189268"},{"date":"16:02 22/06","title":"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-ly-do-giup-dt-phap-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-peru.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Les Bleus gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n c\u00f9ng su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C.</h2><h2>Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Deschamps</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia, HLV Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Peru.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDeschamps \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/155653-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Deschamps c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDeschamps ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 gi\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Australia. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c. Olivier Giroud \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 chia l\u1eeda ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBlaise Matuidi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thay cho Corentin Tolisso. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Kante v\u00e0 Matuidi, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 do h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi Ph\u00e1p ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ch l\u1ea1c h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00eam qua c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u00fac n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1m t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng n\u0103m nay, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn &ldquo;G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng G\u00f4-loa&rdquo; s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 th\u00e9p Umtiti &ndash; Varane</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-phap-vs-peru-463-189178.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span>. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3 hai hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Umtiti v\u00e0 Varane \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Inca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 8 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 ph\u00e1 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Peru t\u1ea1o s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Umtiti v\u00e0 Varane c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 64 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 94 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nUmtiti v\u00e0 Varane \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Kylian Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhung-diem-nhan-Phap-vs-Peru-1-0-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mbappe c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc qu\u00fd ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00eam qua, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft kh\u00f3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Peru ph\u1ea3i ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 4 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00eam qua, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Mbappe c\u00f2n tung ra 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 49 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u1ee9c 84%.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ph\u00e1p g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf kh\u00f3a c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, Mbappe b\u1ed7ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus. V\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0 n\u00e0y, Mbappe th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Peru:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-cua-phap-truoc-peru-421-189255.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-ca-ngoi-kante-sau-tran-thang-truoc-peru-421-189243.html\">Pogba ca ng\u1ee3i Kante sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"461","checkdouble":"189269"}]}